*Hospital Management System - Java*

A comprehensive *Hospital Management System* built in Java that streamlines administrative and medical operations. This modular system includes functionalities for admins, receptionists, laboratory staff, and pharmacists—providing a full workflow from appointment scheduling to billing.

---

## 📌 Features

### 🔐 Login System

* Secure login for Admin, Receptionist, Lab Staff, and Pharmacist roles.

### 🧑‍💼 Admin Panel

* Central control system.
* Manage user accounts and access to all modules.

### 🧾 Receptionist Module

* Schedule and manage patient appointments.
* Record basic patient information.

### 🔬 Laboratory Module

* Receive test requests from the receptionist or doctors.
* Upload and manage patient test results.

### 💊 Pharmacy Module

* Receive medicine prescriptions.
* Dispense medicines to patients.
* Generate billing and receipts.

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

* *Java (Core)* – GUI and application logic
* *JDBC / MySQL* – Backend database connectivity
* *NetBeans / IntelliJ* – Recommended IDE for running the project
